title: Ask HN: What kind of web apps would Martians accessing Earth internet need?
text:
The day humans living on another planet try to check the latest from Hacker News is not far away :P

I'm exploring all the different digital avenues which may get affected in their lives on the new planet.

For e.g. timezones, instant messaging, etc.

What are some digital technologies we would need to make this transition happen for them seamlessly?

Ask HN: Looking for Task Automation?
text:
Do you have a workflow that you would like to automate but don't know how to or don't have the time to?

My friend and I are software engineers at big tech companies, and we want to help folks, especially non-technical folks, become more productive by automating parts of their job. We are just getting started and interested in learning more so we will build for free.

Let's talk, shoot us an email at samspa.dev.pdx at gmail.com
